a:5:{s:5:"title";s:84:"Vendasta Unlimited calling bonus for Conversations AI Premium extended to mid-2026";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:1064:"<p>Conversations AI Premium extended its unlimited calling bonus and now lists it as available until mid-2026. Earlier messaging described the bonus as ending in January 2026.</p>
<h3>What changed</h3>
<p>Unlimited calling bonus: extended → mid-2026.</p>
<p>Overage billing: the product states it will provide advance notice before any overage billing takes effect.</p>
<h3>What didn’t change</h3>
<p>Premium continues to include up to 300 minutes per month of AI voice receptionist usage.</p>
<p>Each call supports up to 10 minutes.</p>
<h3>Why it matters</h3>
<p>For teams planning voice-volume usage, the extension keeps the cost model stable for longer, while the “advance notice” commitment reduces surprise overages during the transition back to metered billing.</p>
<p>Learn more: <a href="https://roadmap.vendasta.com/changelog/unlimited-calling-bonus-for-conversations-ai-premium-extended-until-mid-2026">https://roadmap.vendasta.com/changelog/unlimited-calling-bonus-for-conversations-ai-premium-extended-until-mid-2026</a></p>
";s:9:"text-flow";a:10:{i:0;s:172:"Conversations AI Premium extended its unlimited calling bonus and now lists it as available until mid-2026. Earlier messaging described the bonus as ending in January 2026.";i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:12:"What changed";}i:2;s:47:"Unlimited calling bonus: extended → mid-2026.";i:3;s:107:"Overage billing: the product states it will provide advance notice before any overage billing takes effect.";i:4;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:20:"What didn’t change";}i:5;s:88:"Premium continues to include up to 300 minutes per month of AI voice receptionist usage.";i:6;s:36:"Each call supports up to 10 minutes.";i:7;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:14:"Why it matters";}i:8;s:207:"For teams planning voice-volume usage, the extension keeps the cost model stable for longer, while the “advance notice” commitment reduces surprise overages during the transition back to metered billing.";i:9;s:127:"Learn more: https://roadmap.vendasta.com/changelog/unlimited-calling-bonus-for-conversations-ai-premium-extended-until-mid-2026";}s:4:"meta";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}}s:7:"summary";s:210:"Conversations AI Premium extended its unlimited calling bonus and now lists it as available until mid-2026. Earlier messaging described the bonus as ending in January 2026. | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:9:"tags-data";a:2:{s:5:"ctree";a:3:{i:0;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:33:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";}i:1;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:45:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";}i:2;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:8:"vendasta";s:4:"href";s:38:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/vendasta/";}}s:20:"all-resnames-uploads";a:0:{}}}